{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act46side", "eventName": "雪山降臨1101", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "OS-9", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "凜刃出匣", "storyInfo": "維多利亞大軍壓境，開斯特邀請恩希歐迪斯前往“榮光”號會談。恩雅一行人抵達遺跡，她們離耶拉岡德的真相只有一步之遙。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "45_g8_kjeragstreet", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowfall", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遠方躁動的轟鳴驚醒了樹梢上的寥寥落雪，本該靜謐的街道瀰漫著一絲不祥的溫熱。"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡原本是聖山腳下通往蔓珠院的路，此時卻有維多利亞的部隊橫亙道路中央，履帶碾過路面，毫不避諱地留下不可逾越的障礙。"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戰車上的喇叭傳出清楚的謝拉格語——"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$radio", "channel": "o", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“謝拉格居民們，請勿驚慌，根據維多利亞對目前態勢的決策，我們會保障所有人的安全。”"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“此次行動不會干擾民眾的正常生活，只是建議所有人，在這樣的天氣裡待在家中。”"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“也警告劫持維多利亞人士的不法分子以及相關人士，立刻釋放人質，否則我們會立刻採取行動！”"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "o", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_279_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這位先生，可以讓我過去對面嗎？", "name": "謝拉格老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_279_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想要回家生火，到吃飯的時間了，我的妻子在等著我……", "name": "謝拉格老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_279_1#1$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡已經封鎖了，繞道，或者待在這裡。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_279_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但……我只是想去馬路對面。", "name": "謝拉格老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_279_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您擔心安全，檢查我身上的東西吧，除了食物，沒有別的了。", "name": "謝拉格老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_279_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是蔓珠院的人？", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_279_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不屬於蔓珠院，我只是個鐵匠。", "name": "謝拉格老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_279_1#1$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼繞路，或者待在這裡。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_279_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這條道路我走了幾十年……", "name": "謝拉格老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_279_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老爺爺，不要惹事，沒有好處！", "name": "憂心忡忡的行人"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快點離開那裡吧！聽他的！", "name": "陰沉無奈的行人"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不想再說第三遍。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_279_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "謝拉格老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_279_1#1$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老人蹣跚地離開車隊，回頭望去，妻子也在櫥窗後望著他。"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他搖搖手，讓妻子離開。"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_279_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "耶拉岡德在上……我願聆聽你的盛怒……", "name": "謝拉格老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_279_1#1$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "67_i06", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.1, "yScaleFrom": 1.1, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 45.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們怎敢入侵我們的土地！趕快滾開！聽到了嗎？滾出去！", "name": "怒不可遏的行人"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞人，維多利亞人……這些日子最恨的就是這幾個字。", "name": "憂心忡忡的行人"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……竟然還有人在這時候敢擄他們的人。", "name": "憂心忡忡的行人"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看不出來嗎？這顯而易見只是最卑劣的藉口，維多利亞人來了，謝拉格的天要變了……", "name": "陰沉無奈的行人"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "*謝拉格俚語*，不光袖手旁觀還講這種喪氣話，比餓了三天的馱獸還沒出息，我現在就幫他們認識一下謝拉格！", "name": "怒不可遏的行人"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你要鬧事就離遠一點！別讓他們以為我是跟你一夥的！", "name": "憂心忡忡的行人"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對，對，你去喀蘭貿易，他們不是有保全嗎？", "name": "陰沉無奈的行人"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一群廢物……", "name": "怒不可遏的行人"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "廢物？你有勇氣，你在所不惜，你有家庭嗎？", "name": "陰沉無奈的行人"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果這是談判的結果，如果三大家族、蔓珠院、喀蘭貿易……他們都無所作為，那我們能做什麼？", "name": "陰沉無奈的行人"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "耶拉岡德在上……請原諒我的畏懼，我的膽怯……", "name": "陰沉無奈的行人"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "憤怒、畏懼、不安……各種情緒在手無寸鐵的人群中瀰漫，卻無從撼動他們對面全副武裝的軍隊。"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到他們的聲音被引擎的轟鳴聲淹沒。"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "67_G12_deck", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "animtext", "attributes": {"content": "<p=2>“榮光”號甲板</>", "id": "at1", "name": "group_location_stamp", "style": "avg_only_medium", "pos": "-400,-200", "block": "false", "p": 2.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "animtextclean", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2013_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "閣下，我們的艦隊已經完全包圍了謝拉格雪山入口。", "name": "開斯特親衛隊隊長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2013_1#1$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在謝拉格內部的先遣部隊同樣嚴密包圍了蔓珠院，謝拉格的武裝力量無力對我們發起反抗。", "name": "開斯特親衛隊隊長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2013_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2013_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝拉格的聖女，現在不知所終。不過我們會確保，在她露面的第一時間，就鎖定她的位置。", "name": "開斯特親衛隊隊長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2013_1#4$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事態沒有超出我們的掌控……所以請恕我直言。", "name": "開斯特親衛隊隊長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2013_1#4$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2013_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "閣下，您似乎沒有必要親臨戰場前線。", "name": "開斯特親衛隊隊長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2013_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……不要急躁，菲利帕。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#1$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "注意你的言詞，我應該糾正過，謝拉格並非是我們的敵人，而是值得我們重視的合作夥伴。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#1$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2013_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是喀蘭貿易，到現在還沒有正式回應我們的談判邀請。", "name": "開斯特親衛隊隊長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2013_1#1$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵呵……我能想像。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#8$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩希歐迪斯是個驕傲的人……想來要他消化這樣一場失敗，應該是無比艱難的事吧。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#1$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "菲利帕，你應該多少聽說過他的故事，細算來，他也是你的血親。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#1$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2013_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不理解，如果他當真如傳聞中那樣才學出眾，又為何放棄留在您身邊的機會，甘願埋沒在這片深山中？", "name": "開斯特親衛隊隊長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2013_1#1$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像我說的，他的確是個驕傲的人。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#1$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可以給他一點時間……六個小時。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#1$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果謝拉格官方還是不肯接受我們的協議，那事情就只能以令人遺憾的方式收場了。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2013_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明白。", "name": "開斯特親衛隊隊長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2013_1#1$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是閣下，還有一件不知是否算得上值得在意的小事。", "name": "開斯特親衛隊隊長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2013_1#1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2013_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那位在明面上已經是死人的布朗陶家的家主，我們又發現了她活動的痕跡。", "name": "開斯特親衛隊隊長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2013_1#4$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2013_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "目前她正在黑騎士的保護下藏身在蔓珠院裡。", "name": "開斯特親衛隊隊長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2013_1#1$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……我想在這種時候，恩希歐迪斯不會大費周章地隱藏一個絲毫不重要的人。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#6$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然不值一提……但我不喜歡變數。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#1$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去找到她。找到她在隱藏的東西。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#1$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2013_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遵命，閣下。", "name": "開斯特親衛隊隊長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2013_1#1$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "30_ex1_snowmount", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "收到，我將執行有限度的調遣，等待進一步指示。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "全體注意，一隊守住正面，二隊向北門進發，封鎖那裡，三四隊尋找制高點盯住院內。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有人，嚴陣以待，漏出去一個人，就等著面見公爵。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_soldiersrun", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.5}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "45_g11_karlanheadquarters", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1162_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生，我並沒有收到任何允許維多利亞人進入的命令。", "name": "喀蘭貿易員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1162_1#1$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "充分理解，我們會在此等待回覆。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1162_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總裁已經交代，不接受任何邀約，如果您……", "name": "喀蘭貿易員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1162_1#1$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有關係，我會在這裡耐心等待，就像每一個謝拉格人等待嚴冬過去一樣。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#3$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼謝拉格人準備用什麼方式度過今年的冬天呢？我很好奇。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你或許沒機會親身感受了。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不代表我個人，我的體會也不重要，諾希斯先生。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "平等地給予每個人表達的機會，我相信這種糟糕的狀況下需要這種態度，您說呢？", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你現在還有什麼目的？", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請放心，喀蘭貿易的現任總裁，諾希斯先生。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我這次前來只帶著一個再簡單不過的任務——替公爵閣下向恩希歐迪斯先生發出談判邀約。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是一場簡單的，以維護兩國關係為目的的，和平的談話。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#2$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們公然派遣軍隊包圍了謝拉格，用炮口對準平民，讓士兵封鎖街市。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些都是所謂的和平談判的一部分？", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "諾希斯先生……", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "公爵只是想讓謝拉格真正的主人明白，疾馳的艦船並不在意甲板上的人向何處奔跑，但是對大多數人來說，最好的選擇只有抓穩扶手。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "深刻理解這點的過程可以很漫長，也可以在瞬息之間……取決於閣下已經獲知的“命令”。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不算開門見山，維多利亞人，你應該不需要我來教你該說什麼。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我更願意稱之為“請求”，諾希斯先生，來自維多利亞的請求，如今可不多見。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們誠摯邀請恩希歐迪斯先生，與公爵一道參加關於謝拉格未來的熱切會談。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們會確保會議能順利舉行，公爵也已經下達指示，沒有人會受到任何傷害。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我們同樣有自己的立場——維多利亞必須立即停止一切正在進行的軍事入侵。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很遺憾，這將取決於恩希歐迪斯先生與公爵閣下會談的結果。而我沒有資格代表公爵做出任何承諾。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，我只希望能在足夠溫暖的地方度過這個冬天……一個小小的期望，那會是謝拉格。", "name": "維多利亞大使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2012_1#1$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 1.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_lightsnow", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "30_ex1_snowmount_s", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$monastery_sad_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "text": "人們究竟該以何種面目，去面對祂呢", "x": 180.0, "y": 250.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.001, "width": 700.0, "block": "true", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st2", "text": "我曾問過自己無數次，直到流下歉疚的淚水——因為我找不到答案", "x": 180.0, "y": 320.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.001, "width": 700.0, "block": "true", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st3", "text": "如同現在，我在風雪中踟躕，什麼都尋找不到", "x": 180.0, "y": 420.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.001, "width": 700.0, "block": "true", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st2", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st3", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "text": "喀蘭之心，只是一個故弄玄虛的修辭", "x": 180.0, "y": 250.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.001, "width": 700.0, "block": "true", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st2", "text": "一幅夢中的繪畫，一處山崖間的爛泥", "x": 180.0, "y": 320.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.001, "width": 700.0, "block": "true", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st3", "text": "蔓珠院說，人在瀕臨死亡時，會看見祂的面龐", "x": 180.0, "y": 390.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.001, "width": 700.0, "block": "true", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st4", "text": "我想，這是我最後的機會", "x": 180.0, "y": 460.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.001, "width": 700.0, "block": "true", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st2", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st3", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st4", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "text": "然而，我卻無法向您證明任何事情", "x": 180.0, "y": 250.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.001, "width": 700.0, "block": "true", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st2", "text": "我只看到了篝火旁的母親、窗簾下的妻子", "x": 180.0, "y": 320.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.001, "width": 700.0, "block": "true", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st3", "text": "我本該擁有的生活", "x": 180.0, "y": 420.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.001, "width": 700.0, "block": "true", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st2", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st3", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "text": "您已讀完這位無信的信徒為自己所寫的墓誌銘", "x": 180.0, "y": 250.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.001, "width": 700.0, "block": "true", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st2", "text": "他最後懇求您", "x": 180.0, "y": 320.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.001, "width": 700.0, "block": "true", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st3", "text": "為他拭去碑上的霜雪", "x": 180.0, "y": 420.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.001, "width": 700.0, "block": "true", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st2", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st3", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"layer": 1.0, "fadetime": 2.5}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.2, "fillto": 0.01, "fadetime": 2.5}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.2, "fillto": 0.01, "fadetime": 2.5}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個孤零零的墳墓挺立在路旁，恩雅與阿德頌在這座孤墳前駐足。"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1998_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只埋葬了他。", "name": "阿德頌"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1998_1#1$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1998_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他在臨死前，只來得及為自己刻好墓碑。", "name": "阿德頌"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1998_1#7$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，我們一路上遇到的屍骨，都是……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1998_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人的屍骨。", "name": "阿德頌"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1998_1#1$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只有人才會用價值和意義麻痺自己……為了登上聖山，為了走到祂的身側，見證祂的存在，他們願意獻出生命。", "name": "阿德頌"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1998_1#1$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖女的右手拂過殘損的木碑，完成了墳墓主人的心願。"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "冷風掠過她的指縫，彷彿想讓她抓住什麼，她抬頭望向白雪覆蓋的山脊，耳畔傳來一陣年輕女子的笑聲……"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長老，您有聽見——", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她吞下了疑問，這陣笑聲在山脊間迴響、漸弱，直到成為回憶。"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1998_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒聽見什麼。", "name": "阿德頌"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1998_1#1$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖女大人，請繼續。", "name": "阿德頌"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1998_1#1$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩雅遲疑了一下，點點頭，繼續朝著越發晦暗的天際、厚雪覆蓋的山頂走去。"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "風雪翻湧，牽扯著聖女的衣裝，雪粒掛在眉間，一如掛在她所走過的枯樹。"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "30_ex1_snowmount_s", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#8$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你再用力一點，光靠我拉你是跟不上恩雅的——", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼，呼……不就，兩步路的事，跟那麼緊幹嘛……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#18$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……對了。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#18$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛才，他們在這裡，對著什麼在說話是不是？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#18$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……我好像也看到了。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這裡除了雪和山石之外什麼都沒有……唉，不管那麼多了。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "150,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "150,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃琳娜勉強踏出幾步，而踩過的雪地正泛出幽藍的螢光。"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "與此同時，她隱隱覺得有人正在注視著自己，但身邊只有抱著她的手臂、咬著牙的茱安娜。"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "風吹得頭腦麻木了，這肯定是什麼錯覺。當心中閃過這個念頭時，埃琳娜聽到了一聲嘆息。"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "67_G7_cave", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1998_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……您主動走進了一個必敗的賭局。", "name": "阿德頌"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1998_1#1$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖女大人。", "name": "阿德頌"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1998_1#1$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡就是……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1998_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正是。", "name": "阿德頌"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1998_1#1$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1998_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "群山深處……“喀蘭之心”的所在。", "name": "阿德頌"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1998_1#7$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "150,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩雅，我完成你給的任務，把她拖過來了！", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（壓低聲音）到了到了，別愣著。", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#4$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#8$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "150,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 2.5}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.5}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……等等，這，不對，絕不是這樣！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃琳娜用力搖頭，她拍拍臉，提起大大小小的儀器對著洞壁上下探查。"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是一個在謝拉格隨處可見的普通山洞，靠近聖山的頂峰似乎是它唯一的特別之處，恩雅往更深處走去，呼吸也稍稍急促。"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最深處到洞口只有一百公尺，寬度勉強夠五、六個人站成一排，苔蘚和地衣薄薄地覆蓋岩石，空氣中混雜真菌和泥土的味道，瀰散著濕潤的腥氣。"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1998_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們不是最早想要尋找到祂的人，甚至我也不是……", "name": "阿德頌"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1998_1#7$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1998_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我年輕時的夙願，便是目睹祂的真容，真正跪倒在祂面前。為此，我在藏經閣翻遍每一本書，讀盡每一行詩歌，尋覓祂存在的證據。", "name": "阿德頌"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1998_1#1$1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "許多前人也留下過各種記錄與辨析，有人提到過這裡，聖山上唯一的洞窟。", "name": "阿德頌"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1998_1#1$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1998_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我踏過崎嶇漫長的山路，終於來到這裡……", "name": "阿德頌"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1998_1#3$1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "記載中，曾經有蔓珠院修士前往聖山深處避難。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#4$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1998_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正是如此。", "name": "阿德頌"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1998_1#1$1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您或許還記得，那一位喚醒了耶拉岡德的聖女的故事。", "name": "阿德頌"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1998_1#1$1"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……傳說中，耶拉岡德降下天罰，蔓珠院先後挑選了一百名少女上山祈福，最後的那位少女平息了祂的怒火。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#10$1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而真相是，最後的那位少女，是某位家族族長的女兒，因此引發了各大家族聯合圍攻蔓珠院。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1998_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那場屠戮中，倖存下來的修士逃到這裡，接著就是所謂“神蹟”降臨，謝拉格恢復和平。", "name": "阿德頌"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1998_1#1$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您又會如何解釋那次“神蹟”？", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1998_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看看如今的謝拉格，答案不言而喻，誰聽說過能毫無理由戛然而止的戰爭？", "name": "阿德頌"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1998_1#8$1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "連謀殺少女都能成為崇高的“神蹟”，那麼政治妥協當然也能被改編成宗教傳說。", "name": "阿德頌"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1998_1#8$1"}, {"id": 380, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謀殺……長老如此看待蔓珠院當初的舉動……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1998_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，以謀殺求得慰藉，任由心被愚昧所驅使，這是蔓珠院為“耶拉岡德”背負的血債。", "name": "阿德頌"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1998_1#7$1"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有可以擔保永恆的神明，我們所走的每一步都如履薄冰，不可不慎。", "name": "阿德頌"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1998_1#7$1"}, {"id": 385, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1998_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖女大人，我已帶您驗明耶拉岡德的真相……", "name": "阿德頌"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1998_1#8$1"}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在……無論您想掙扎多久，老朽都能等下去。", "name": "阿德頌"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1998_1#8$1"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩雅！你快來看！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最深處的這堆石頭，不像是天然形成的，簡直就像是堆砌成的一道門牆。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 394, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1998_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……過去的修士想把這裡建設成避難所，無論發現什麼都不稀奇。", "name": "阿德頌"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1998_1#1$1"}, {"id": 398, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也就是說……在這扇“門”的背後，很有可能就是當年蔓珠院修士的藏身所，也是隱藏了謝拉格無數秘密的所在……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#12$1"}, {"id": 400, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1998_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更有可能的是，當你打開這扇門後，發現其中空無一物。", "name": "阿德頌"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1998_1#8$1"}, {"id": 402, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就容我們見證，長老。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1"}, {"id": 404, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1998_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿德頌"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1998_1#1$1"}, {"id": 406, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖女半闔著雙眼，她從滔滔不絕演說歷史的老人身前走過，逐漸接近洞窟的盡頭。"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "深深呼吸，讓身子緊貼著盡頭的洞壁，像是一個久違的擁抱。"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "泥土染上了雙手與臉頰，髮梢下露出苔痕，她彷彿是在大地上沉睡……"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……感覺到了。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1"}, {"id": 420, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩雅，探測器顯示，在這一層很單薄的岩壁背後，似乎存在一個巨大的空洞。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是這裡沒有別的入口……如果需要的話，我可以炸開它。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 426, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，你怎麼敢對聖地——", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#6$1"}, {"id": 428, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "動手吧。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2010_1#1$1"}, {"id": 432, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊——恩雅？！", "name": "茱安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_4211_snhunt_1#10$1"}, {"id": 437, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "耶拉岡德在上……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 439, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了真相，原諒我的無禮吧……！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 440, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}